{"tid":874720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[埋單計數] 月薪3萬以下不適合搭高鐵","createTime":"2018-10-24T11:50:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T15:35:54.000Z","uid":37232,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b50dc6fcd17ef3e985309852c70cd22f44fecd98","tid":874720,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T11:50:02.000Z","msg":"高鐵建造成本: $864億<br />\n高鐵首月平均每日乘客: 5萬<br />\n高鐵壽命, 無數據, 本人估50年<br />\n<br />\n香港01(親中)測試乘搭高鐵和直通巴士由尖沙咀地鐵站到廣州上下九路結果<br />\n<br />\n高鐵車費和時間: $257.34, 4小時20分鐘 (4.33hrs)<br />\n直通巴士車費和時間: $105.5, 5小時8分鐘(5.13hrs)<br />\n<br />\n其相差車費和時間為 $151.84, -0.8hrs<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">用時薪去睇, 此乘客要認為每小時值$189.8先會搭高鐵 ($189.8/hr)</span><br />\n有此人工的乘客應5天工作和每日返8小時, 用每月返20天計, 即<span style=\"color: red;\">月薪為$30368</span><br />\n<br />\n再計埋建造成本和總節省時間<br />\n<br />\n50年內, 總節省時間為 50年 x 365.25天 x 5萬人次 x 0.8小時 = 7.305億小時<br />\n即每小時成本為$118.28/hr<br />\n<br />\n夾埋之前$189.8/hr, 即<span style=\"color: red;\">月薪為$49292的人搭高鐵先回到本</span><br />\n<br />\nPS. 無考慮營運成本"},{"pid":"a1d32472be173f45a30fb08087e0e1f6f75fa7ec","tid":874720,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T10:08:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bf7ed7afe58e382ac00b15e11272abfa2be7c59","tid":874720,"uid":6869,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T10:22:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a8d9f7fc48e6bdc93f0d73d517b6e2e4b3897a57","tid":874720,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T15:35:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}